@host = http://localhost:8080
@accessToken = REPLACE_ME
@notificationId = 1

### =========================
### Notification - List
### GET /api/notifications
### =========================
GET {{host}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### =========================
### Notification - Unread Count
### GET /api/notifications/unread-count
### =========================
GET {{host}}/api/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### =========================
### Notification - Detail
### GET /api/notifications/{notificationId}
### =========================
GET {{host}}/api/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### =========================
### Notification - Mark as Read (single)
### PATCH /api/notifications/{notificationId}/read
### =========================
PATCH {{host}}/api/notifications/{{notificationId}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### =========================
### Notification - Mark All as Read
### PATCH /api/notifications/read-all
### =========================
PATCH {{host}}/api/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}